title: First Week Onboarding
description:
We spent the first week on the My Onboarding Journey, where we made a deep dive on Cisco's ins and outs, such as the company's culture, guidelines and general tools and platforms of which all employees depend on. 

 - Participated in activities meant to learn Cisco's history and its technologies. 

 - Since this event happened in all EMEA, we had the opportunity to meet Cisco employees from all over the world.
